  "_comment": "Static Big-O reference for the Native family (Unity.Collections 2.1.4). Schema matches complexity.json: keyed by <Collection>_<Op>, time/space, amortized/avg where relevant. Native containers live on the UNMANAGED (native) heap, not the GC heap, so the 'space' here is native allocation; managed GC Allocated is ~0 for every op (the headline). 'this[k]' / TryGetValue / Contains on the hash containers are open-addressing avg-O(1). Build (增) ops capacity is pre-sized to N so growth is amortized away.",
